descriptionHtml:
The Fixie are going shopping, they like market games! Choose a shopping list, pick up goods and count money at the cash desk! This is grocery shopping games for boys and girls! 😜 🛒

Shopping can be a lot of fun for little child! Let’s go to the supermarket and buy some tools in the game “The Fixies: Supermarket Games!” 🛒

What will you do in these games:
🛒 Choose a character to go shopping with one of the Fixies!
🛒 Get the shopping list of the tools you need to buy in the market games with Fixie!
🛒 Just grab the required items one by one and put them into the shopping cart!
🛒 It's the grocery shopping games for kids, and if you take the wrong tool, that’s no problem. Just put it back onto the shelf! 🤗
Toddler, do you remember where the necessary tools are? Speed up the cart and get it faster!
🛒 If your shopping cart is full, go to the cash register and pay for the purchases! Count carefully to pay no extra money! 👛

Bright colorful and user-friendly interface will make this app one of your favorite children's games very fast! This family games for boys and girls master motor skills, learn to count, and who knows – probably soon they will be helping you in a real supermarket!

😜 Get ready in the Fixie shop games!
The Fixies love inventing things, and they need a lot of tools. Will you help them and buy some things in the games for 4 year olds? This is a real fun kids game free and also a great way of learning motor skills, how to be an attentive child and how to count in games for six year olds.

🔍 Are you looking for a games with your little child? Congratulations, you find one of the interesting grocery shopping games! These are not standard market games for boys and girls, it's a real fun kids game free! But these cool kid games for 4 year olds will please children of any age and for babies, too! 🧒 Let them try it in this shopping games for kids.

📲 “The Fixies: Supermarket Games!” - it's almost a real shop games for six year olds child!
